                    <ab></ab>
                    <ab>(C.) In nomine sancte individueque trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/173">Otto</persName> divina providente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator </rs>augustus. Si ratis nostrorum fidelium
                        peticionibus asensum prebemus, promciores eos in nostro fore obsequio minime
                        titubamus. Quocirca omnium sancte dei ecclesia fidelium nostrorumque
                        presentium scilicet ac futurorum comperiat industria, qualiter interventu
                        atque consultu amantissime nostre <rs key="#marriage"
                            >coniugis</rs>
                        <persName key="#Queen #marriage" ref="#people/1301"
                            >Adheleide</persName> nostrique <rs key="#Queen">imperii consortis</rs>
                        per hanc nostri precepti paginam concedimus donamus atque largimur <persName
                            key="#Count #fidelisOf" ref="#people/1302">Aimoni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">commiti</rs> dilectoque nostro <rs key="#fidelisOf"
                            >fideli</rs>
                        <rs key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive">corticulas
                            duas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fiscal_property">iuris regni nostri</rs> in <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/131"><placeName key="#Cities"
                                ref="#places/106">Vercellensi</placeName></geogName>
                        <rs key="#Comitatus">commitatu</rs> coniacentus que <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive"
                            ref="#estates/1203"><placeName key="#Villages/settlements"
                                ref="#places/210">Andurni</placeName></geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive"
                            ref="#estates/1204"><placeName key="#Villages/settlements"
                                ref="#places/537">Molinaria</placeName></geogName> nominantur, una
                        cum capellis villis massaritiis rupibus planiciebus terris cultis et
                        incultis aquis molendinis piscationibus aldionibus et aldiabus utriusque
                        sexus familiis districtis publicisque vectigalibus et pensionibus omnibusque
                        que dici vel nominari possunt ad predictas corticulas in integrum
                        pertinentibus, nec non et a nostro iure et dominio in prefati comitis ius et
                        dominium omnino transfundimus et delegamus. Insuper hac nostra preceptali
                        auctoritate confirmamus et corroboramus eidem fideli nostro omnes res et
                        utriusque sexus familias iuris sui, videlicet <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property">cortes</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property" ref="#estates/1205"><placeName
                                key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/48"
                            >Alice</placeName></geogName>, <geogName key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property"
                            ref="#estates/1206"><placeName key="#Villages/settlements"
                                ref="#places/329">Cavaliaga</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property" ref="#estates/1207"><placeName
                                key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/825"
                            >Casanova</placeName></geogName>, <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/1208"><placeName key="#Villages/settlements"
                                ref="#places/1605">Ropoli</placeName></geogName> in Vercellensi
                        commitatu coniacentes atque <geogName key="#Curtes"><placeName
                                key="#Villages/settlements">Caxana</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property" ref="#estates/1209"><placeName
                                key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/1603">Bremitu
                                Ticinense</placeName></geogName>, <geogName key="#Curtes"><placeName
                                key="#Villages/settlements">Zentiano</placeName></geogName>,
                            <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/97"><placeName
                                key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/101"
                            >Astelliano</placeName></geogName>, <geogName key="#Curtes"><placeName
                                key="#Villages/settlements">Gomarasca</placeName></geogName>,
                            <geogName key="#Curtes"><placeName key="#Villages/settlements"
                                >Caldanaxo</placeName></geogName>, <geogName key="#Curtes"
                                ><placeName key="#Villages/settlements"
                            >Calvarengo</placeName></geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property" ref="#estates/1210"><placeName
                                key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/1604"
                                >Frassinetu</placeName></geogName> in <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/143"><placeName key="#Villages/settlements"
                                ref="#places/255">Lomellensi</placeName></geogName>
                        <rs key="#Comitatus">commitatu</rs> scitas, una cum castellis villis
                        capellis massaritiis vineis campis insulis aquis molendinis piscationibus
                        districtis pensionibus aldionibus et aldiabus servis et ancillis omnibusque
                        que dici vel nominari possunt ad predictas curtes et res pertinentibus in
                        integrum. Preterea si de predictis rebus a nobis concessis et de pretaxatis
                        a nobis confirmatis legales querimonie contra eum orte fuerint aut de carum
                        terminis litigaverint, hac nostra imperiali auctoritate concedimus ei, ut
                        per inquisitionem et sacramentum trium liberorum hominum liceat eum
                        affirmare quod iure proprietario inde investitus fuerit et eas firmiter
                        tenuerit, ac deinde habeat teneat firmiterque possideat ipse suique heredes
                        habeantque potestatem tenendi donandi vendendi commutandi pro anima
                        iudicandi et quicquid eorum decreverit animus fatiendi, omnium hominum
                        contradictione remota. Si quis igitur contra hanc nostri precepti paginam
                        ire temptaverit aut infringere presumpserit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras centum</rs>, medietatem camere nostre
                        et medietatem predicto comiti suisque heredibus. Quod ut verius credatur
                        diligentiusque ab omnibus observetur, manu propria roborantes annulo nostro
                        subter iussimus insigniri. Signum domni Ottoni invictissimi imperatoris (M.)
                        augusti. <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Liutgerus"
                            >Liutgerius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> advicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1303">Guidonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi Data III. Kalendas
                        ianuarii anno dominice incarnationis DCCCCLXIII, indictione VI, anno imperii
                        serenissimi Ottonis imperatoris primo; actum <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Domus" ref="#places/65">Papie</placeName>. </ab>
                </div>
